## 1. Clean code · Código directo

|        |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
| ------ | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **EN** | Keep components readable. No helpers, intermediate variables, or props used only once unless they add real clarity. Put Tailwind classes and `aria-label` directly in JSX (`className`, `clsx`). Never store Tailwind classes, `image sizes`, or technical config in data files. Avoid legacy bloat (mega-components, useless `variant`/`theme`, `className` in data). |
| **ES** | Código legible en el componente. Sin helpers, variables intermedias ni props de un solo uso sin claridad real. Clases Tailwind y `aria-label` directos en el JSX (`className`, `clsx`). No guardar clases Tailwind, `image sizes` ni config técnica en data. Evitar herencias infladas (mega-componentes, `variant`/`theme` innecesarios, `className` en data).        |

---

## 2. Atomic design · Diseño atómico

|        |                                                                                                                                                    |
| ------ | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **EN** | Follow **atoms → molecules → organisms** so one file does not do everything. Split when a component has too many responsibilities.                 |
| **ES** | Respetar **atoms → molecules → organisms** para no sobrecargar un solo archivo. Dividir cuando un componente acumule demasiadas responsabilidades. |

| Level · Nivel | Path · Ruta                       | Role · Rol                                  | Examples · Ejemplos                                       |
| ------------- | --------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------- |
| Atom          | `common/*/components/atoms`       | Single responsibility · Una responsabilidad | `ActionButton`, `ServiceCardDetailsButton`, `NavbarBrand` |
| Molecule      | `features/*/components/molecules` | Combines atoms · Combina atoms              | `DashboardShellHeader`, `DashboardMetricsColumn`          |
| Organism      | `features/*/components/organisms` | Layout sections · Secciones del layout      | `DashboardLayout`, `HomeDashboard`                        |

---

## 3. Data vs UI · Datos vs UI

|        |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
| ------ | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **EN** | **Business content & config** → `src/utils/data/static/pages/` (`homeAssets`). **Styles, layout, icons, structure** → components in `common/` or `features/`. **No component** (atom, molecule, or organism) may hardcode site text: labels, titles, descriptions, placeholders, `aria-label`, `alt`, CTAs, etc. All copy comes from `homeAssets` via props. Organisms (or top layout) import data and pass `copy` / `config` down.                               |
| **ES** | **Contenido y config de negocio** → `src/utils/data/static/pages/` (`homeAssets`). **Estilos, layout, iconos y estructura** → componentes en `common/` o `features/`. **Ningún componente** (atom, molecule u organism) puede hardcodear texto del sitio: labels, títulos, descripciones, placeholders, `aria-label`, `alt`, CTAs, etc. Todo sale de `homeAssets` por props. Los organisms (o layout superior) importan y reparten `copy` / `config` hacia abajo. |

