## 5. Call actions · Acciones

| Component      | EN                                                    | ES                                                |
| -------------- | ----------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------- |
| `ActionButton` | Native button (no link) — visible `text`              | Botón nativo (sin link) — `text` visible          |

|        |                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
| ------ | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **EN** | **Links** (`<a>`) → `text-body md:text-body-md lg:text-body-lg`. **Labels / eyebrows / meta** → `text-small md:text-small-md lg:text-small-lg`. Do not mix link scale with label scale. |
| **ES** | **Enlaces** → `text-body md:text-body-md lg:text-body-lg`. **Labels / eyebrows / meta** → `text-small md:text-small-md lg:text-small-lg`. No mezclar escala de enlaces con la de labels.                            |

