## 8. DOM & layout discipline · DOM y layout sin inventiva

|        |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
| ------ | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **EN** | **No invented structure.** Do not add wrapper `motion.div` / `span` **only** to attach `ref` or `className` when a native element (`button`, `input`, Next `Link`) can take `ref` and classes directly. Do **not** add `createPortal`, React `Context` providers, or split components (Provider / Trigger / Panel) unless the **current** DOM in this repo cannot achieve the result with normal composition. Before overlays / dropdowns / width alignment: identify the **positioned containing block** (`fixed`, `relative`, …). Match existing files in this repo; do not paste patterns from unrelated codebases. |
| **ES** | **Sin estructura inventada.** No añadir envoltorios **solo** para `ref` o `className` si el elemento nativo admite `ref` y clases. **No** `createPortal`, `Context` ni Provider/Trigger/Panel salvo necesidad real. Identificar el **bloque de posicionamiento** antes de overlays. Alinear con archivos existentes; no pegar patrones de otros proyectos.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |

---

## Quick reference · Referencia rápida

| Topic · Tema                | Do · Hacer                                                                    | Don't · Evitar                                                                     |
| --------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Copy · Texto                | `homeAssets` → props                                                          | Hardcode in JSX                                                                    |
| Colors · Colores            | `@theme` tokens (`bg-white`, `text-ink`, `bg-violet`, …)                      | `#hex`, `rgb`, `bg-[#…]`, role names that clash with Tailwind (`accent` for pink)  |
| Shadows · Sombras           | `shadow-nav`, `shadow-panel`, `shadow-flyout`, `shadow-control`              | `--shadow-*` in `@theme`, raw `box-shadow`, `shadow-{color}` expecting a composite |
| Typography · Tipografía     | `text-body md:… lg:…` / `text-small md:…` / `DashboardTitle`                  | `text-[…]`, links on `text-small`                                                  |
| Overlay · Overlay           | `bg-overlay`                                                                  | Inline gradients in JSX                                                            |
| Structure · Estructura      | atoms / molecules / organisms                                                 | One overloaded component                                                           |
| Styling · Estilo            | Tailwind in JSX                                                               | Classes in data files                                                              |
| Actions                     | `ActionButton` / native `<a>` where needed                                    | One component for both                                                             |
| DOM / layout · DOM / layout | `ref` on `button`/`Link`; `absolute` under same `nav`                         | Wrappers only for `ref`; duplicate `fixed` + `calc`; Portal/Context (§8)           |
